List of DBs running in PSQL:-
===========================
Use \l or \l+ in psql to show all databases in the current PostgreSQL server

Find Configuration file:-
[postgres@lnx0901 ~]$ psql -d analytics_prod_01
psql (11.2)
Type "help" for help.

analytics_prod_01=# SHOW config_file;
              config_file
----------------------------------------
 /var/lib/pgsql/11/data/postgresql.conf
